 observable results---iron\nfluorescence line profiles---from the theory of black hole accretion with\nalmost no phenomenological assumptions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Apr 2016 03:43:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-27"}
